title: SPY+ Presents: MC, K-Dub and Cairoli. Just Another Day On The Ranch
description: Filthy does not do this video justice. Nasty doesn't do it justice either. Filthy McNasty might be a tastier way to say the day we just spent on Jeremy McGrath's ranch was monuMENTAL. Jeremy asked us at SPY+ if we would help get a freeride track set up and we literally jumped at the chance. We also figured that we would throw Kevin Windham and Antonio Carolli into the mix for gits and shiggles. The end result... MonuMENTALly Filthy.
